<Recipe
  title="Homemade Pumpkin Spice Latte"
  description="Make your own semi-traditional pumpkin spice latte at home"
  slug="pumpkin-spice-latte"
  publishedDate="2019-10-01"
>
  <h1 class="post-title">Homemade Pumpkin Spice Latte</h1>
  <p>Make your own pumpkin spice latte at home</p>

  <div class="post-main">
    <div class="blog-body">
      <h4>Prep</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>1 cup milk</li>
        <li>2 Tablespoons pureed pumpkin</li>
        <li>1½ Tablespoons sugar</li>
        <li>½ Tablespoon pure vanilla extract</li>
        <li>
          ½ teaspoon pumpkin pie spice (additional to taste)
          <ul>
            Don't have pumpkin pie spice? Make your own!
            <li>3 parts ground cinnamon</li>
            <li>2 parts ground ginger</li>
            <li>2 parts ground nutmeg</li>
            <li>1 large dash of allspice (optional)</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h4>Let's do it</h4>
      <ol>
        <li>Simmer all ingredients together</li>
        <li>Mix with as many shots of espresso as you'd like, or simply pour into coffee</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>
</Recipe>
